ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder replacing “the Minister of State (Seniors)” with “the Minister of Employment and Social Development”
PrecisOrder Amending the schedule to Order in Council P.C. 2007-281 of March 2, 2007, as amended by Order in Council P.C. 2018-787 of June 14, 2018, Order in Council P.C. 2018-1027 of July 18, 2018 and Order in Council P.C. 2023-770 of July 26, 2023, by replacing “the Minister of State” with “the MINISTER OF EMPLOYMENT AND SOCIAL DEVELOPMENT” in the portion of section 1 before paragraph (a), subsections 2(1) and (2), and section 4.
